title: Episode 209 I Got the Power (Feat. Gillie Da King & Wallo267)
itunes:title: Episode 209 I Got the Power (Feat. Gillie Da King & Wallo267)
description:
Philly Rapper Gillie da King and Wallo267 join the ladies of Lip Service this week. The guys speak on what it's like being male strippers and the double standards that come along with it. Angela asks what's the most disrespectful thing to ever happen during sex...and Gillie's answer will make you cringe. Ask Yee questions were sent in and discussed, as well as how guys feel getting their ass slapped. Enjoy!
